                           <pdfaProperty:description>Values for Journal Article Version are one of the following:
AO = Authorâ€™s Original
SMUR = Submitted Manuscript Under Review
AM = Accepted Manuscript
P = Proof
VoR = Version of Record
CVoR = Corrected Version of Record
EVoR = Enhanced Version of Record</pdfaProperty:description>
